{"tid":2289923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒系列38: 本港最新失業率維持6.4%","createTime":"2020-11-17T14:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-17T14:56:52.000Z","uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6dfdb52d485b0b1211ef2218c7cfd807402a79c5","tid":2289923,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-17T14:56:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560504-20201117.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560504-20201117.htm&d=gkHqMR5YDMJAUJmZ80XM40B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=767d0b69\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560504-20201117.htm&h=9480a0a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560504-20201117.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府最新公布本港8月至10月失業率，維持在6.4%，與7月至9月的數字一樣，而就業不足率亦維持在3.8%，失業人數就減少約2000人。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，勞工市場情況仍然困難，但這段期間本地疫情呈現進一步穩定的跡象，整體經濟情況在最近幾個月見到一些改善，但僱主的招聘意欲應將會依然審慎，勞工市場在短期內仍將會面對壓力，政府會繼續密切留意相關情況。"}]}